android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO.description: Allows application to access the audio record path.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS.info: use the authentication credentials of an account
android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS.description: Allows an application to request authentication tokens.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

manifest_analysis.title:
App has a Network Security Configuration
[android:networkSecurityConfig]
manifest_analysis.desc: The Network Security Configuration feature lets apps customize their network security settings in a safe, declarative configuration file without modifying app code. These settings can be configured for specific domains and for a specific app.
manifest_analysis.name: App has a Network Security Configuration [android:networkSecurityConfig]

manifest_analysis.desc: A Service is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. "GDPR_account_check_popup_msg" : "We collect personal information, including your email address and name to create your KineMaster account.

Collected email addresses and names are used for user identification, and can be used to transfer information such as app updates, new items etc. as needed.

We also collect device identifiers, item downlaods, and purchase information that occurs when you use KineMaster. Device identifiers are used for the purpose of limiting the number of available terminals for each user. Item download and purchase information is used for checking purchase details, refunding items, and redownloading items. The collected data will not be used in outside of the purposes mentioned above. Information is collected and used while the account is in use. . For more information, please refer to our Privacy Policy.

If you do not agree to these terms, you will not be able to create a user account. If you do not create a user account, you will be able to use the app as normal, however some features will be limited.

Do you agree to the provision and use of your personal information to create an account?"

"kinemaster_for_samsung_details" : "Thank you for downloading KineMaster for Samsung. As an exclusive benefit for Samsung users, through August 2018 we are pleased to offer the first month free for monthly subscriptions, and a discounted price for both monthly and annual subscriptions.
 
 As usual, you are welcome to try KineMaster for free for as long as you like. To purchase the full version with the discount, which removes the "Made with KineMaster" watermark and provides access to premium assets in the Asset Store, simply tap the delete icon next to the watermark when you are editing a project."
"km30beta_expired_message" : "ขอบคุณที่ทดลองใช้งาน KineMaster 3 เวอร์ชันเบต้านี้ ตัวเบต้าเวอร์ชันนี้ได้หมดอายุการใช้งานแล้ว โปรดเช็ค Google Play สำหรับเวอร์ชันที่ใหม่กว่า"
"km30beta_firsttime_message_a" : "ขอบคุณที่เข้ามามีส่วนร่วมกับการทดสอบของ KineMaster 3.0, ความเห็นและข้อเสนอแนะของคุณมีประโยชน์มาก และจะช่วยในการพัฒนา KineMaster ต่อไป"
"km30beta_firsttime_message_b" : "บางความสามารถซึ่งใช้ได้หลังจากเป็นสมาชิก สามารถใช้งานได้โดยไม่เสียค่าใช้จ่ายในช่วงทดสอบเบต้า"
"km30beta_firsttime_message_c" : "เนื่องจากตัวโปรแกรมเป็นเวอร์ชันเบต้า คุณอาจพบกับข้อผิดพลาดหรืออาการค้างต่างๆ หากคุณเห็นปุ่ม แจ้ง คุณช่วยเราได้โดยการใช้มัน"
"km30beta_firsttime_message_d" : "ด้วยความขอบคุณอย่างสุดซึ้งจากทีมงาน KineMaster"
"km30beta_firsttime_title" : "ยินดีต้อนรับ"

"km30beta_reenter_message" : "ขอบคุณที่ทดลองใช้งาน KineMaster 3 เวอร์ชันเบต้านี้ โปรดอย่าลืมตรวจสอบสำหรับอัปเดทเวอร์ชันใหม่ๆ บน Google Play หากคุณพบเจอปัญหาในการใช้งานใดๆ โปรดแจ้งกลับมายัง support@kinemaster.com หรือแหล่งชุมชนสำหรับผู้ทดสอบ KineMaster 3.0 เบต้า บน Google Plus"
"km3xbeta_expired_message" : "ขอขอบคุณที่ทดลองใช้ KineMaster รุ่นเบต้า โปรแกรมรุ่นเบต้านี้หมดอายุแล้ว โปรดตรวจสอบเวอร์ชันล่าสุดได้ใน Google Play"
"km3xbeta_firsttime_message_a" : "ขอขอบคุณที่เข้าร่วมโครงการ KineMaster รุ่นเบต้า ข้อคิดเห็นและคำแนะนำของคุณมีค่าอย่างมาก เพราะช่วยเราให้สามารถปรับปรุง KineMaster ได้อย่างต่อเนื่อง"
"km3xbeta_firsttime_message_b" : "เนื่องจากเป็นซอฟต์แวร์เบต้า คุณอาจเจอปัญหาอุปกรณ์แฮงก์หรือความผิดพลาดอื่นๆ ถ้าคุณเห็นปุ่มรายงานปัญหา เราอยากให้คุณใช้ปุ่มนี้"
"km3xbeta_firsttime_message_c" : "ถ้าต้องการยกเลิกการเข้าร่วมโครงการเบต้าและกลับไปใช้โปรแกรมเวอร์ชันจริง โปรดเข้าไปที่เพจ ทดสอบแอปฯ ใน Google Play โดยใช้ปุ่ม สมัคร/ยกเลิกสมัคร ด้านล่าง"
"km3xbeta_firsttime_message_d" : "ขอขอบคุณล่วงหน้าจากทีมงาน KineMaster"

"permission_content_camcorder_primary" : "หากต้องการใช้ฟังก์ชันบันทึกวิดีโอ KineMaster จำเป็นต้องสามารถเข้าถึงกล้องและไมโครโฟนในอุปกรณ์ของคุณเพื่อบันทึกวิดีโอและเสียง ขั้นตอนนี้สามารถเลือกใช้หรือไม่ก็ได้ (คุณยังสามารถใช้แอปฯอื่นๆเพื่อบันทึกวิดีโอแทนได้) แต่คุณต้องให้สิทธิก่อน หากคุณต้องการบันทึกวิดีโอโดยตรงจาก KineMaster"
"permission_content_camcorder_secondary" : "คุณสามารถเปิดการเข้าถึงกล้องและไมโครโฟนสำหรับ KineMaster ได้ ภายใต้ แอปฯ ในการตั้งค่าอุปกรณ์ของคุณ"

"permission_content_audio_record_primary" : "आवाज रिकॉर्डिंग की कार्यक्षमता प्रदान करने के लिए, KineMaster को आपके उपकरण के माइक्रोफ़ोन तक पहुंचने में सक्षम होना चाहिए। यह वैकल्पिक है, लेकिन यदि आप सीधे KineMaster में ध्वनि रिकॉर्डिंग करना चाहते हैं, तो आपको अनुमति देनी होगी।"
"permission_content_audio_record_secondary" : "आप अपनी उपकरण सेटिंग्स में एप्लिकेशन के तहत KineMaster के लिए माइक्रोफ़ोन एक्सेस सक्षम कर सकते हैं।"

"permission_content_camcorder_primary" : "वीडियो रिकॉर्डिंग की कार्यक्षमता प्रदान करने के लिए, KineMaster को वीडियो और ऑडियो रिकॉर्डिंग के लिए आपके उपकरण के कैमरा और माइक्रोफ़ोन तक पहुंचने में सक्षम होने की आवश्यकता है। यह वैकल्पिक है (आप इसके बजाय कैमकॉर्डिंग के लिए किसी अन्य ऐप का उपयोग कर सकते हैं), लेकिन आपको अनुमति देनी होगी अगर आप सीधे KineMaster में कैमकॉर्डिंग करना चाहते हैं।"
"permission_content_camcorder_secondary" : "आप अपनी उपकरण सेटिंग्स में एप्लिकेशन के तहत KineMaster के लिए कैमरा और माइक्रोफ़ोन एक्सेस सक्षम कर सकते हैं।"

"permission_content_camera_primary" : "फ़ोटो लेने के लिए, KineMaster को अपने उपकरण के कैमरे तक पहुंचने में सक्षम होना चाहिए। यह वैकल्पिक है (आप इसके बजाय फोटो लेने के लिए दूसरे ऐप का उपयोग कर सकते हैं), लेकिन आप KineMaster में सीधे तस्वीरें लेना चाहते हैं, तो आपको अनुमति देनी होगी।"
"permission_content_camera_secondary" : "आप अपनी उपकरण सेटिंग्स में ऐप्स के तहत KineMaster के लिए कैमरा एक्सेस सक्षम कर सकते हैं।"
"permission_content_phone_primary" : "Allow KineMaster to access Phone Calls for Ads and In_App Billing?"
"permission_content_phone_secondary" : "You can allow KineMaster to access Phone Calls in Settings > Apps > App Permissions."

"permission_content_storage_primary" : "वीडियो संपादन कार्य प्रदान करने के लिए, KineMaster को परियोजनाओं में जोड़ने के लिए वीडियो, फोटो, ऑडियो और अन्य मीडिया को एक्सेस करने और परियोजनाओं से निर्यात किए गए रेंडर वीडियो को सहेजने के लिए, परियोजनाओं को खोलने और सहेजने के लिए आपके उपकरण के संग्रहण तक पहुंचने में सक्षम होना चाहिए। KineMaster कार्य करने के लिए संग्रहण पहुंच की आवश्यकता है।"

"permission_mic_settings" : "एक्सेस को अनुमति देने के लिए, कृपया नीचे एप जानकारी को टैप करें, और अनुमतिओं के तहत, माइक्रोफोन अनुमति चालू करें।"

"kinemaster_for_samsung_details" : "Thank you for downloading KineMaster for Samsung. As an exclusive benefit for Samsung users, through August 2018 we are pleased to offer the first month free for monthly subscriptions, and a discounted price for both monthly and annual subscriptions.
 
 As usual, you are welcome to try KineMaster for free for as long as you like. To purchase the full version with the discount, which removes the "Made with KineMaster" watermark and provides access to premium assets in the Asset Store, simply tap the delete icon next to the watermark when you are editing a project."
"km30beta_expired_message" : "Thank you for trying this beta version of KineMaster 3.0. This beta version has expired. Please check Google Play for an updated version."

"km30beta_reenter_message" : "Thank you for trying this beta version of KineMaster 3.0. Please be sure to frequently check Google Play for updated version. If you experience any issues, please report them to support@kinemaster.com or on the KineMaster 3.0 Beta tester community on Google Plus."

"km3xbeta_firsttime_message_a" : "Cảm ơn bạn đã tham gia chương trình beta KineMaster đang diễn ra. Phản hồi và các đề xuất của bạn cực kỳ có giá trị và sẽ giúp chúng tôi tiếp tục cải tiến KineMaster."

"km3xbeta_firsttime_message_b" : "Với bất kỳ phần mềm beta nào, bạn cũng có thể trải qua những hỏng hỏng hoặc các lỗi khác. Trong trường hợp hỏng hóc, nếu bạn nhìn thấy nút báo cáo, chúng tôi khuyến khích bạn sử dụng nút này."

"km3xbeta_firsttime_message_c" : "Để không tham gia chương trình beta và trở về phiên bản sản xuất, vui lòng vào xem trang Thử nghiệm Ứng dụng trên Google Play bằng cách sử dụng nút Tham gia/Không tham gia dưới đây."

"permission_content_audio_record_primary" : "Để cung cấp tính năng ghi âm giọng nói, KineMaster cần được truy cập micrô của thiết bị. Việc này là tùy chọn nhưng bạn phải cho phép nếu bạn muốn thực hiện ghi âm giọng nói trực tiếp trong KineMaster."
"permission_content_audio_record_secondary" : "Bạn có thể bật truy cập micrô cho KineMaster tại mục Ứng dụng trong phần cài đặt thiết bị của bạn."

"permission_content_camcorder_primary" : "Để cung cấp chức năng quay video, KineMaster cần được truy cập vào máy ảnh và micrô của thiết bị để quay video và thu âm thanh. Việc này là tùy chọn (bạn có thể sử dụng một ứng dụng khác để quay video) nhưng bạn phải cho phép nếu bạn muốn thực hiện quay phim trực tiếp trong KineMaster."
"permission_content_camcorder_secondary" : "Bạn có thể bật truy cập camera và micrô cho KineMaster tại mục Ứng dụng trong phần cài đặt thiết bị của bạn."

"permission_content_camera_primary" : "Để chụp ảnh, KineMaster cần được truy cập vào máy ảnh của thiết bị. Việc này là tùy chọn (bạn có thể sử dụng một ứng dụng khác để chụp ảnh) nhưng bạn phải cho phép nếu bạn muốn chụp ảnh trực tiếp trong KineMaster."
"permission_content_camera_secondary" : "Bạn có thể bật truy cập máy ảnh cho KineMaster tại mục Ứng dụng trong phần cài đặt thiết bị của bạn."
"permission_content_phone_primary" : "Allow KineMaster to access Phone Calls for Ads and In_App Billing?"
"permission_content_phone_secondary" : "You can allow KineMaster to access Phone Calls in Settings > Apps > App Permissions."

"permission_content_storage_primary" : "Để cung cấp các chức năng chỉnh sửa video, KineMaster cần được truy cập vào bộ nhớ của thiết bị để mở và lưu các video được biên tập hiệu ứng, truy cập video, hình ảnh, âm thanh và các phương tiện truyền thông khác để thêm chúng vào video được biên tập và lưu video kết xuất đồ họa được xuất ra từ các video được biên tập. Việc truy cập bộ nhớ được yêu cầu bắt buộc để KineMaster hoạt động."
"permission_content_storage_secondary" : "Bạn có thể bật truy cập bộ nhớ cho KineMaster tại mục Ứng dụng trong cài đặt thiết bị của bạn."
"permission_mic_settings" : "Để cho phép truy cập, vui lòng gõ Thông tin Ứng dụng dưới đây, và theo các Quyền hạn, hãy bật quyền hạn micrô."
"permission_mic_title" : "Cho phép KineMaster truy cập micrô của bạn để ghi âm giọng nói?"

"permission_storage_rationale" : "KineMaster cần có thể truy cập các video, ảnh chụp, phương tiện và tệp trên thiết bị của bạn để cung cấp các chức năng chỉnh sửa video. Vui lòng cho phép KineMaster truy cập bộ lưu trữ trên thiết bị của bạn."

"permission_storage_settings" : "KineMaster cần có thể truy cập các video, ảnh chụp, phương tiện và tệp trên thiết bị của bạn để cung cấp các chức năng chỉnh sửa video Để cho phép truy cập vào bộ lưu trữ trên thiết bị của bạn, vui lòng gõ vào mục Thông tin Ứng dụng dưới đây, và theo các quyền hạn, hãy bật quyền hạn Bộ lưu trữ."

"GDPR_account_check_popup_msg" : "Nós coletamos informações pessoais, incluindo seu endereço de e-mail e nome, para criar sua conta KineMaster. 
 
 Os endereços de e-mail coletados e nomes são usados ​​para identificação do usuário e podem ser usados ​​para transferir informações, como atualizações do Google Apps, novos produtos etc. se fosse necessário. 
 
 Também coletamos identificadores de dispositivos, downloads de produtos e informações de compra que podem ocorrer ao usar o KineMaster. Identificadores de dispositivo são usados ​​para limitar o número de terminais disponíveis por usuário. Downloads de produtos e informações de compra são usados ​​para verificar detalhes de compra, devoluções e re-downloads de produtos. Os dados coletados não serão usados ​​além dos propósitos mencionados acima. As informações são coletadas e usadas enquanto a conta está ativa. Para mais informações, consulte nossa Política de Privacidade. 
 
 Se você não concordar com esses termos, não poderá criar uma conta de usuário. Se você não criar uma conta de usuário, poderá usar o Aplicativo normalmente, mas alguns recursos serão limitados.

"GDPR_account_check_popup_msg" : "Wir erfassen personenbezogene Daten, einschließlich Ihrer E-Mail-Adresse und Ihres Namens, um Ihr KineMaster-Konto zu erstellen.

Gerätekennungen werden verwendet, um die Anzahl verfügbarer Endgeräte für jeden Benutzer zu begrenzen. Informationen zum Herunterladen und Kaufen von Artikeln werden verwendet, um Kaufdetails zu überprüfen, Artikel zu refundieren und Artikel erneut zu laden. Die gesammelten Daten werden nicht außerhalb der oben genannten Zwecke verwendet. Informationen werden gesammelt und verwendet, während das Konto verwendet wird. . Weitere Informationen finden Sie in unserer Datenschutzrichtlinie. 
 
 Wenn Sie diesen Bedingungen nicht zustimmen, können Sie kein Benutzerkonto erstellen. Wenn Sie kein Benutzerkonto erstellen, können Sie die App wie gewohnt nutzen, einige Funktionen sind jedoch eingeschränkt.

playstore_details.title: KineMaster - Video Editor, Video Maker
playstore_details.description:
KineMaster is a full-featured video editor for Android. KineMaster has powerful tools that are easy to use, like multiple video layers, blending modes, voiceovers, chroma key, speed control, transitions, subtitles, special effects, and so much more! Find out why creators love KineMaster for YouTube, TikTok, and Instagram and why journalists, educators, marketers, and vloggers use it professionally! Download KineMaster to create, edit, and share your own amazing videos!

    
Features

• Multiple layers of video, images, stickers, special effects, text, and handwriting 
• Reverse your videos for a unique look
• Blending modes to create startling, beautiful effects
• Add voiceovers, background music, voice changers, and sound effects 
• Editing tools to trim, splice, and crop your video 
• The Asset Store provides music, clip graphics, fonts, stickers, transitions, and more to enhance your video, updated weekly 
• Speed control for time lapse and slow motion effects 
• EQ presets, ducking, and volume envelope tools for immersive audio 
• Keyframe animation tool to add motion to layers 
• Export 4K 2160p video at 30FPS 
• Apply different color filters to make your video stand out 

 • Share on YouTube, Facebook, Dropbox and more
 • Many, many more features, options, and settings!
    

Subscription
  
KineMaster and all of its editing tools are free to use. This also includes unlimited exports in resolutions up to 4K.  When you subscribe to KineMaster Premium, you remove the watermark, unlock professional tool presets, and get access to over a thousand premium assets in the KineMaster Asset Store. Subscribe to KineMaster today Premium within the app!   

Subscriptions to KineMaster Premium automatically renew unless you cancel in Google Play.  

For more details, questions and feature requests, please contact us: Tap on the question mark button on the KineMaster main screen, then tap E-mail support!
